passages.tootipText1:
Average enter: the sum of the real-time cumulative enter of all shopping centers divided by the number of shopping centers 
Peak enter: the maximum value of the peak enter in all shopping centers 
Peak occupancy: the maximum value of the peak occupancy in all shopping centers 
Today's occupancy: the sum of the occupancy in all shopping centers
passages.tootipText2:
Average enter today: the cumulative enter divided by the number of business hours 
Peak enter today: the maximum enter from the start of business hours to the current time 
Peak occupancy today: the maximum number of people staying in the shopping center and the time point from the start of business hours to the current time 
Peak occupancy today: the difference between the total incoming enter and the total outgoing enter from the start of business hours to the current time
passages.tootipText3:
Average enter: the cumulative enter of all shopping centers in the selected time period divided by the number of shopping centers 
Total enter: the sum of enter of all shopping centers in the selected time period 
Peak enter: the maximum value of peak enter in all shopping centers in the selected time period 
Peak passenger volume: the maximum value of peak enter in all shopping centers in the selected time period 
Effective enter flow : the sum of the unique number of passengers in all shopping centers in the selected time period 
Sales: the sum of the sales in all shopping centers in the selected time period
passages.tootipText4:
The drainage map includes entrance and exit introduction passenger flow, store introduction passenger flow, radiation store passenger flow and departure passenger flow, Among them: 
Incoming passenger flow at the entrance and exit: the transformed passenger flow directly entering the selected store from the entrance and exit 
Incoming passenger flow at the store: the transformed passenger flow from other stores to the selected store 
Radiating store passenger flow: the transformed passenger flow from the selected store to other stores 
Departure passenger flow: the passenger flow directly leaving the shopping center from the selected store
passages.tootipText5:
1. Trend chart: shows the passenger flow trend of entrances and exits and shops respectively 
2. Import total passenger flow: the sum of passenger flow from entrances and exits and shops 
3. Number of entrances and exits: the total number of entrances and exits entities 
4. Number of stores: the total number of store entities
passages.tootipText6:
1. Trend chart: shows the trend of passenger flow converted from the selected entity to other stores 
2. Radiated total passenger flow: the sum of passenger flow radiated from the selected store to other stores 
3. Radiated stores: the total number of selected stores radiated to other stores
passages.tootipText7:
Total passenger flow: the sum of passenger flow in the selected time period 
Peak passenger flow: the maximum passenger flow and time point in the selected time period 
Peak passenger volume: the maximum number of people staying in the shopping center and time point in the selected time period 
Effective passenger flow: the only passenger flow of users in the shopping center in the selected time period 
Sales: the sum of sales in the shopping center in the selected time period 
Floor efficiency : sales in the selected time period divided by the area of the shopping center 
 transaction rate: the number of transaction orders in the shopping center in the selected time period divided by the passenger flow entering the shopping center 
 customer unit price: the sales in the shopping center in the selected time period divided by the number of transaction orders in the shopping center
